text: Nia Imani Franklin (born July 27, 1993) is an American beauty pageant winner and Miss America 2019. Born in Winston-Salem, North Carolina, Franklin moved to New York City in 2017. In June 2018, she was crowned Miss New York 2018. On September 9, 2018, she was crowned Miss America 2019 in Atlantic City, New Jersey.
